We are looking for individuals who can work both at the conceptual as well as the implementation level, and who are able to work with a small and multi-disciplinary team. The qualified candidate will have the opportunity to contribute to the research phase, prototyping and final production design. You will be responsible for delivering UX concepts, interaction flows, visual designs, and design requirements.<br />
